; Regression test for issue #524: --lots do not subtract when price precision is small
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/524
; When a lot price has many decimal places (e.g. 1.026087 EUR), ledger fails to
; combine buy and sell lots. Instead of showing 8.00 APPL (23 - 15), it shows the
; lots separately as 23.00 APPL and -15.00 APPL.

commodity APPL
    note Apple
    format 1,000.00 APPL

commodity EUR
    note Euro
    format 1,000.00 EUR

2017-01-20 Buy Apple
    Broker:Stock                       23 APPL @@ 23.6 EUR
    Openning:Balance

2017-11-28 Sell Apple
    Broker:Stock                        -15 APPL {1.026087 EUR} [2017-01-20] @@ 24.00 EUR
    Broker:Profits

test bal broker --lots
23.00 APPL {1.026087 EUR} [2017/01/20]
-15.00 APPL {1.026087 EUR} [2017/01/20]
           15.39 EUR  Broker
           15.39 EUR    Profits
23.00 APPL {1.026087 EUR} [2017/01/20]
-15.00 APPL {1.026087 EUR} [2017/01/20]    Stock
--------------------
23.00 APPL {1.026087 EUR} [2017/01/20]
-15.00 APPL {1.026087 EUR} [2017/01/20]
           15.39 EUR
end test
